 Actions in Playwright( which are perform on locator )


| Method                            | Whatdoes                                                         

| `locator.check()`                  | Checks a checkbox (if not already checked).                            
| `locator.click()`                  | Clicks on the element.                                               
| `locator.dblclick()`               | Double-clicks on the element.                                        
| `locator.setChecked()`             | Explicitly sets checkbox to checked or unchecked based on a boolean. |
| `locator.tap()`                    | Simulates a tap (used mostly in mobile emulation).                   
| `locator.uncheck()`                | Unchecks a checkbox.                                                 
| `locator.hover()`                  | Moves the mouse over the element (useful for tooltips, dropdowns).   |
| `locator.dragTo()`                 | Drags one element to another.                                        
| `locator.screenshot()`             | Takes a screenshot of the element.                                   
| `locator.fill()`                   | Fills an input or textarea with text.                                
| `locator.clear()`                  | Clears the input field.                                              
| `locator.selectOption()`           | Selects an option in a `<select>` dropdown.                          
| `locator.selectText()`             | Selects (highlights) the text inside an input or textarea.           
| `locator.scrollIntoViewIfNeeded()` | Scrolls the element into view if itâ€™s not already visible.           
| `locator.blur()`                   | Removes focus from the element.                                      
| `locator.dispatchEvent()`          | Dispatches a custom DOM event.                                       
| `locator.focus()`                  | Focuses the element (like clicking into a textbox).                  
| `locator.press()`                  | Simulates pressing a key on the element.                             
| `locator.pressSequentially()`      | Presses a sequence of keys, one by one.                              
| 'locator.setInputFiles()'        | Uploads files via`<inputtype="file">`.                             
